    retrofit:evidence "RESOLVED 2026-07-21: crates/ggen-engine/tests/reasoner_independence_e2e.rs is a REAL file (both_engines_sync_a_gated_pack_to_identical_outputs, violating_fixture_is_refused_under_both_engines -- both run and PASS 2026-07-21) proving exactly the cited property. The prior 'zero matches' finding searched for a literal function name equal to the file name; the file/module itself was never missing. .specify/memory/constitution.md's citation and packs/ggen-constitution-pack/ontology.ttl's LawXII ccn:note both corrected to name the real file and its two actual function names precisely." .

retrofit:UnmechanizedLawsDisclosed a retrofit:SPOF ;
    rdfs:label "9 laws (not 3) explicitly mechanized=false, every one with a named gap" ;
    retrofit:standing "Accepted" ;
